'''再力花'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Thalia dealbata''；{{lang-en|Powdery thalia}}，Hardy canna，Powdery alligator-flag）為[[竹芋科|竹芋科]][[水竹芋屬|水竹芋屬]]下的一個種。原產於[[美國南部|美國南部]]和中部及[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]的一種[[水生植物|水生植物]]<ref>Fraser, John. 1794. Icon. Thalia dealbata t. 1, ''Thalia dealbata'' (the publication apparently lost but the illustrations still surviving at the British Museum in London fide Tropicos)</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/766823#page/368/mode/1up |title=Roscoe, William. 1807.  Transactions of the Linnean Society of London 8: 340, ''Thalia dealbata''  |accessdate=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2020-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200218092420/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/766823#page/368/mode/1up |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/7430545#page/405/mode/1up |title=Rafinesque, Constantine Samuel. 1838.  Flora Telluriana 4: 51. ''Spirostylis biflora'' |accessdate=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924220843/http://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/7430545#page/405/mode/1up |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.yuanlin.com/flora/HTML/Info/2006-5/Yuanlin_Flora_1771.HTML|title=再力花|3=|publisher=中國園林網|accessdate=2014-06-10|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304194147/http://www.yuanlin.com/flora/HTML/Info/2006-5/Yuanlin_Flora_1771.HTML|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://bonap.net/MapGallery/County/Thalia%20dealbata.png |title=Biota of North America Program, map, ''Thalia dealbata'' |accessdate=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2014-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714130939/http://bonap.net/MapGallery/County/Thalia%20dealbata.png |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[溫哥華|溫哥華]]這樣的北方地區也可以生存<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=1&taxon_id=222000385 |title=Flora of North America v 22, ''Thalia dealbata'' |accessdate=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304071359/http://www.efloras.org/florataxon.aspx?flora_id=1&taxon_id=222000385 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://plants.usda.gov/java/profile?symbol=THDE |title=USDA Profile |accessdate=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2013-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505152433/http://plants.usda.gov/java/profile?symbol=THDE |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.wildflower.org/plants/result.php?id_plant=thde |title=University of Texas Native Plant Database |accessdate=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024153823/https://www.wildflower.org/plants/result.php?id_plant=thde |dead-url=no }}</ref>。另有資料顯示，再力花與其他同屬植物相比分布比較偏北。它是竹芋科中唯一分布於北美洲的種類，它的原產地不是熱帶，但是在熱帶與溫帶的花園中都能生長，所以美國不少地方的公園水池中都會栽種。冬天的時候，它在水中的根莖不會凍死可以度過溫帶的冬天。<ref>{{Cite web|title=科博館全球資訊網植物園：塗粉的鱷魚旗－水竹芋|url=https://www.nmns.edu.tw/public/BotanicalGarden/flowers/2009/summer/980728.htm|accessdate=2019-07-21|author=|date=2008-09-03|last=|format=|work=科博館|publisher=|language=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190721055107/https://www.nmns.edu.tw/public/BotanicalGarden/flowers/2009/summer/980728.htm|archive-date=2019-07-21|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

再力花高約{{convert|6|ft|m}}，開紫羅蘭色小花，圓錐花絮，長{{convert|8|in|cm}}。葉子為披針形、呈藍綠色、邊緣為紫色<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ces.ncsu.edu/depts/hort/consumer/factsheets/water-garden/marginalaq/thalia_dealbata.html|title=Marginal Aquatics: Thalia dealbata|last=Evans|first=Erv|publisher=North Carolina State University|accessdate=15 May 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100719130045/http://www.ces.ncsu.edu/depts/hort/consumer/factsheets/water-garden/marginalaq/thalia_dealbata.html|archivedate=2010年7月19日|df=}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.missouribotanicalgarden.org/gardens-gardening/your-garden/plant-finder/plant-details/kc/a646/thalia-dealbata.aspx |title=Missouri Botanical Garden |accessdate=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2013-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922073506/http://www.missouribotanicalgarden.org/gardens-gardening/your-garden/plant-finder/plant-details/kc/a646/thalia-dealbata.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

